name: Madspraycanmutant Odd ver
description:
This illustration come from my custom toy base on platform #madspraycanmutant which was showcased at New York Comic Con last week. From the name of this character, I have a concept of wanting to make this character more "mad", by adding sharp nails and some visual identity of my character.

This version of the toy was sold out, so I made nft.

*See #madcspraycanmutant to see the original base form.
